I have tried using the tools and they are not removing the content that needs to be removed.  I cannot find any phone numbers or email addresses, so I am trying this route.  Inadvertantly 3 medical record word documents were shared.  These documents have been removed from the server, but they are still showing up in the cache and have personal information on it that needs to be removed.  This information has legal ramifications and needs to be removed immediately.  When I search for "Integrative Medicine Consultants, Clear Lake, 4shared" three documents are at the top.  When you click on the link, it takes you to 4shared and an invalid link message, but the information is still on the cache.  I have used the tools to remove it and my pending requests disappeared, but all of the information is still there.  Please help me.  I need this information removed as quickly as humanly possible.  When adding the url below, they are all three the same when I click on them to copy, so it will only take one.  Please let me know if there is some other way I can access this information.  I cannot provide you with access to an authorized example of the work because it is confidential medical records.
